image_analysis.description: An image of a completed OGE Form 278e, specifically Part 6: Other Assets and Income, for the filer Donald J. Trump. The page is numbered 36 of 51 and details various assets, their values, income types, and income amounts. The information is reported as of April 15, 2017.

The main body is a table with columns for asset number, description, EIF, value, income type, and income amount. A footer at the bottom provides the reporting date and a document identifier.
